<div id="review_8760215" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/8760215" />
    <a title="Marcia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/654321-marcia"><img alt="Marcia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1210954181p2/654321.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/8760215?book_show_action=true">Nov 06, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marcia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marcia" href="/user/show/654321-marcia">Marcia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">everyone</span></div>

        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer8760215" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8715653814279475523">I was really impressed by this book, and I&apos;m definitely going to do my part to help the FairTax get signed into law and the income tax repealed. I knew the IRS was bad, but I had no idea how wasteful and unfortunate the income tax is until I read this book. It doesn&apos;t matter what your politics are, at the very least this book will make you rethink your support of the income tax.</span>
  <span id="freeText8715653814279475523" style="display:none">I was really impressed by this book, and I'm definitely going to do my part to help the FairTax get signed into law and the income tax repealed. I knew the IRS was bad, but I had no idea how wasteful and unfortunate the income tax is until I read this book. It doesn't matter what your politics are, at the very least this book will make you rethink your support of the income tax.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8715653814279475523" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


