              <span id="reviewTextContainer125374970" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16554040661263468328">Taxes are, unfortunately, a fact of life. After reading this book I am convinced that the FairTax is a much more reasonable way to collect federal taxes than the current system. I like the fact that the proposed system is very simple, transparent and does not play favorites with any demographic. <br/><br/>I encourage everyone to read this book and urge your elected representatives to make FairTax a reality.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


