<div id="review_28149590" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/28149590" />
    <a title="C." class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/244684-c"><img alt="C." src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1185999263p2/244684.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/28149590?book_show_action=true">Jul 24, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="C." class="user" itemprop="url" name="C." href="/user/show/244684-c">C.</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer28149590" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer640973668103683895">I would support the idea of a National Sales Tax alternative to the current payroll tax system. However, this book was very poorly written and filled with too much &quot;big cats in Washington&quot; rhetoric. I would like to check out a more balanced view of this subject.</span>
  <span id="freeText640973668103683895" style="display:none">I would support the idea of a National Sales Tax alternative to the current payroll tax system. However, this book was very poorly written and filled with too much "big cats in Washington" rhetoric. I would like to check out a more balanced view of this subject.</span>
